## Customization

### Adding New Indicators

1. **Add HTML element:**
```html
<div class="indicator-card">
    <div>
        <div class="indicator-name">Your Indicator</div>
        <div class="indicator-value" id="your-indicator">...</div>
    </div>
</div>
```

2. **Fetch data in JavaScript:**
```javascript
const yourData = await fetchFREDData('SERIES_ID');
document.getElementById('your-indicator').innerHTML = `${yourData.toFixed(2)}%`;
```

3. **Find FRED series IDs:** https://fred.stlouisfed.org/

### Adding New Charts

1. Create canvas element in HTML
2. Use Chart.js to create visualization
3. Fetch time series data from FRED API
4. Update chart with real data

